import React from 'react'
import { BrowserRouter as Router, Switch, Route } from 'react-router-dom'
import { Login, MainApp, Register } from '../../pages'


const Routes = () => {
  return (

    <Router>
      <Switch>
        <Route path='/login'>
          <Login />
        </Route>
        <Route path='/register'>
          <Register />
        </Route>
        <Route path='/'>
          <MainApp />
        </Route>
      </Switch>
    </Router>

  )
}

export default Routes
